Package: simulepidemictrait
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of Pathogen Trait Evolution During an Epidemic
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-09-07
Author: Venelin Mitov
Maintainer: <venelin.mitov@bsse.ethz.ch>
Description: This package provides functions to simulate the chain of transmission events emerging during
  an epidemic outbreak together with the within host evolution of several quantitative trait loci in the pathgogen
  genome associated with a pathogen trait. 
License: GPL (>=2.0)
Depends: ape, data.table
